{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a fully editable Shopify theme section called “Complaint Cards”.
    
    Design:
    - Full-width section with editable background color
    - Centered heading at the top
    - Under the heading: 4 rounded white cards
    - Desktop layout: 4 cards in one row
    - Tablet layout: 2 cards per row
    - Mobile layout must be adjustable in the theme editor:
      - Option 1: 1 card per row
      - Option 2: 2 cards per row / 2x2 layout
    - Each card contains editable text and a small round X icon at the bottom
    - Clean premium ecommerce style, similar to a modern travel product page
    
    Theme editor settings:
    Add settings for:
    - Section background color
    - Heading text
    - Heading color
    - Heading font size desktop
    - Heading font size mobile
    - Heading font weight
    - Heading max width
    - Heading spacing below
    - Card background color
    - Card text color
    - Card border radius
    - Card padding desktop
    - Card padding mobile
    - Card text font size desktop
    - Card text font size mobile
    - Card text line height
    - Card minimum height desktop
    - Gap between cards
    - X icon background color
    - X icon color
    - X icon size
    - Mobile layout selector: “1 per row” or “2 per row”
    - Section padding top desktop
    - Section padding bottom desktop
    - Section padding top mobile
    - Section padding bottom mobile
    - Container max width
    
    Blocks:
    Create repeatable card blocks, max 4 blocks.
    Each block needs:
    - Card text, rich text field so some words can be bold
    - Optional show/hide X icon
    
    Default heading:
    Nog steeds gedoe met overvolle, onhandige tassen? Wij snappen je.
    
    Default cards:
    1. Een zware koffer door drukke straten slepen? Geen pretje.
    2. Je favoriete outfits thuislaten omdat er geen ruimte is? Herkenbaar.
    3. Aankomen met gekreukte kleding terwijl je er juist goed uit wilt zien?
    4. Extra betalen voor ruimbagage? Dat geld besteed je liever op reis.
    
    Default styling:
    - Section background color: #f7f0eb
    - Card background color: #ffffff
    - Heading color: #251b1b
    - Card text color: #111111
    - X icon background color: #382928
    - X icon color: #ffffff
    - Desktop heading font size: 34px
    - Mobile heading font size: 28px
    - Desktop card text size: 17px
    - Mobile card text size: 16px
    - Card border radius: 14px
    - Desktop grid: 4 columns
    - Tablet grid: 2 columns
    - Mobile default: 1 column, but adjustable to 2 columns
    - Make sure the section is fully responsive and does not squeeze the text too much on mobile., Make the white card spacing more adjustable.
    
    Add theme editor settings for:
    - Card padding top
    - Card padding bottom
    - Card padding left/right
    - Mobile card padding top
    - Mobile card padding bottom
    - Mobile card padding left/right
    - Card minimum height desktop
    - Card minimum height mobile
    
    Right now there is too much empty space above and below the text/icons inside the cards. I want to be able to make the cards more compact from the Shopify theme editor.
    
    Also make sure the X icon stays near the bottom left, but the card height and inner spacing can be reduced without breaking the layout.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-complaint-cards-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.section_bg_color }};
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.padding_top_desktop }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.padding_bottom_desktop }}px;
  }

  .ai-complaint-cards-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.container_max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .ai-complaint-cards-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size_desktop }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.heading_font_weight }};
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin: 0 auto {{ block.settings.heading_spacing_below }}px;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.heading_max_width }}px;
  }

  .ai-complaint-cards-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.card_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-complaint-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_bg_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.card_padding_top_desktop }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.card_padding_bottom_desktop }}px;
    padding-left: {{ block.settings.card_padding_horizontal_desktop }}px;
    padding-right: {{ block.settings.card_padding_horizontal_desktop }}px;
    min-height: {{ block.settings.card_min_height_desktop }}px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .ai-complaint-card-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.card_text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.card_text_font_size_desktop }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.card_text_line_height }};
    margin: 0 0 auto 0;
  }

  .ai-complaint-card-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.x_icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.x_icon_size }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.x_icon_bg_color }};
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.icon_spacing_top }}px;
  }

  .ai-complaint-card-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: calc({{ block.settings.x_icon_size }}px * 0.5);
    height: calc({{ block.settings.x_icon_size }}px * 0.5);
    stroke: {{ block.settings.x_icon_color }};
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-complaint-cards-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-complaint-cards-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding-top: {{ block.settings.padding_top_mobile }}px;
      padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.padding_bottom_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-complaint-cards-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_font_size_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-complaint-cards-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      {% if block.settings.mobile_columns == '1' %}
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      {% else %}
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      {% endif %}
    }

    .ai-complaint-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding-top: {{ block.settings.card_padding_top_mobile }}px;
      padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.card_padding_bottom_mobile }}px;
      padding-left: {{ block.settings.card_padding_horizontal_mobile }}px;
      padding-right: {{ block.settings.card_padding_horizontal_mobile }}px;
      min-height: {{ block.settings.card_min_height_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-complaint-card-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.card_text_font_size_mobile }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-complaint-cards-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-complaint-cards-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
      <h2 class="ai-complaint-cards-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {{ block.settings.heading }}
      </h2>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="ai-complaint-cards-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.card_1_text != blank %}
        <div class="ai-complaint-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-complaint-card-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.card_1_text }}
          </div>
          {% if block.settings.card_1_show_icon %}
            <div class="ai-complaint-card-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.card_2_text != blank %}
        <div class="ai-complaint-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-complaint-card-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.card_2_text }}
          </div>
          {% if block.settings.card_2_show_icon %}
            <div class="ai-complaint-card-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.card_3_text != blank %}
        <div class="ai-complaint-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-complaint-card-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.card_3_text }}
          </div>
          {% if block.settings.card_3_show_icon %}
            <div class="ai-complaint-card-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.card_4_text != blank %}
        <div class="ai-complaint-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-complaint-card-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.card_4_text }}
          </div>
          {% if block.settings.card_4_show_icon %}
            <div class="ai-complaint-card-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

